U Instantly, a shimmering, ethereal blue light erupts from the card, focusing on a swirling, abstract representation of various drink containers – a half-empty beer bottle, a sparkling wine glass, a mug of coffee, and a cocktail shaker – all subtly blurred as if viewed through a hazy dream. A young, thoughtful-looking wizard stands slightly to the side, gazing intently at the scene with a wistful expression.  Detailed magical energy weaves around the drinks, conveying the "Scry" effect.  Style: Painterly, slightly surreal, vibrant colors.